---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="DUI / DWI Education - The WEL Foundation">
  <div class="container" style="padding: var(--spacing-8) 0;">
    <header class="reveal-on-scroll" style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8); text-align:center; max-width: 800px; margin-inline: auto;">
      <div style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3);">🚘</div>
      <h1 style="font-size: 3rem; color: var(--color-primary-blue); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3);">DUI / DWI Education</h1>
      <p style="font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
        Navigating the legal aftermath of an impaired driving charge is stressful. Our state-certified programs provide a judgment-free environment to fulfill your court or Motor Vehicle Administration (MVA) requirements quickly and affordably.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: var(--spacing-6); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8);">
      <article class="card reveal-on-scroll stagger-1">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-primary-light-blue);">12-Hour Program</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-main); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3);">
          The standard AEP (Alcohol Education Program) mandated for first-time offenders who are not deemed high-risk by initial assessments.
        </p>
        <ul style="color: var(--color-text-muted); padding-left: var(--spacing-4); line-height: 1.6;">
          <li>Typically spans across 6 successive weeks (2 hours per week)</li>
          <li>Focus on physiological effects of alcohol/drugs</li>
          <li>Legal ramifications and decision-making frameworks</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="card reveal-on-scroll stagger-2">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-primary-light-blue);">26-Hour Program</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-main); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3);">
          An extended curriculum designed for subsequent offenders or individuals whose Blood Alcohol Content (BAC) met enhanced penalty thresholds.
        </p>
        <ul style="color: var(--color-text-muted); padding-left: var(--spacing-4); line-height: 1.6;">
          <li>Includes the foundational 12-hour AEP curriculum</li>
          <li>Additional 14 hours of intensive outpatient counseling</li>
          <li>Individualized risk assessment and mitigation planning</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
      
      <article class="card reveal-on-scroll stagger-3" style="background-color: var(--color-bg-offset);">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-primary-light-blue);">State Compliance</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-main); line-height: 1.7;">
          Upon successful completion of either program, we automatically submit your certification directly to the Maryland MVA and relevant court systems via secure portals, ensuring your legal standing is updated promptly without administrative delays.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <section class="reveal-on-scroll" style="text-align: center; max-width: 600px; margin-inline: auto;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; color: var(--color-primary-blue); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3);">Enroll Today</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);">
        We offer flexible evening and weekend classes to accommodate your work schedule. Contact our front desk to complete your initial assessment and register for an upcoming cohort.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn">View Contact Options</a>
    </section>

  </div>
</Layout>
